===Etymology===
French ''[[dent]]s de [[lion]]'' "teeth of lion"

===Pronunciation===
*(US) {{IPA|/ˈdændiˌlaɪən/}}
*{{audio|en-uk-dandelion.ogg|Audio (UK)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-both}}

# {{countable}} A well-known plant of the genus [[Taraxacum]] ([[T. officinale]], formerly called [[T. Dens-leonis]] and [[Leontodos Taraxacum]]) bearing large, yellow, [[compound flower]]s, and deeply notched leaves.
# {{uncountable}} (''colour'') a [[yellow]] colour, like that of the flower.
